176 A.3d 215 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. LUIS HERNANDEZ, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-387 September Term 2017

080195 November 30, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003402-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
